title: Algorytm miłości
overview: Participants in the series parody Algorytm miłości put their fate in the hands of artificial intelligence to find a perfectly matched love and win the program. Find out how much you can do for reach, fame and money!The new series from the creators of The Office PL is not only a sharp parody of reality, but of the entire entertainment and mass entertainment. Because although sometimes it is embarrassing to admit it, we all love it.
